      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Dangerous attitudes and beliefs of outside territories, in particular
    that of bordering regions, put our residents at risk, something we do not wish
    to encounter.

    However, we also wish to change these attitudes for the better,
    and know our amazing residents do too.

    We ensure anyone who leaves properly
    understands these risks, will co-operate strictly with our supervision, and could
    have a chance of making an impact on visited areas.

'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ab72a9c75c8230a4b9c3ea02b05222c8, type: 2}
